Anyone is welcome to post any star wars ksp content here(Including tv shows such as TCS, rebels, and the mandalorian) . does stuff about star wars is great, and so is KSP, so lets blend them together! 

Also, if you are wondering, my profile pic is not a regular clone captain, nor Captain Fordo. Not many people know this ARC but I will give a hint. He has a mandalorian name that you old republic fans will know.

And yes I have returned from my long leave. In that time I have played Squadrons, Battlefront 2, and Fallen Order. I also watched rebels and TCW over my leave. I continue to scour Wookiepedia of clone troopers:)
